							<article class="message-body js-selectToQuote">
								
								<div class="bbWrapper"><div style="text-align: center"><b><span style="font-size: 18px">H<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'">ello,</span></span></b>&#8203;</div><br />
<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><span style="font-size: 15px">Before starting the topic, I have a detail to bring : I'm <b>French</b>. So, please don't be strict with me if <b>I speak English not very well</b>. Thanks.</span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><span style="font-size: 15px">I <b>like</b> play in this apocalyptic Minecraft server so much. However, I found many details that can be <b>improved</b> or simply <b>added</b> to Decimation and its servers. Here are my <b>ideas and suggestions</b> :</span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><span style="font-size: 15px">-  Change the <b>clan interface</b>. Display <b>clans that are allies or ennemies with us</b><br />
- <b> Decorate the houses</b> in the spawn<br />
-  Add <b>grenades</b> (or Attack items) <b>dealer</b><br />
-  Add more <b>close combat weapons</b> such as a <b>nailed bat</b>, a <b>katana</b> (very rare item), a <b>combat knife</b> or a <b>machete</b>.<br />
-  Add a <b>close combat weapons dealer</b><br />
-  Add <b>more vehicles</b> such as a barricaded car, a van or an helicopter (or more planes types)<br />
-  Add <b>nuclear zones</b><br />
-  Be able to <b>find fortification blocks more easily</b><br />
-  Add a <b>French version</b> for server releases announcements</span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><span style="font-size: 15px">Thank you for reading the ideas I have for Decimation. <b>Sorry for my language quality in English</b>, I try to improve that every day. See you a next time !</span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><span style="font-size: 18px"><b>Takazaki</b></span></span></div>
